{"tid":251589,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"吳克儉出訪英國倫敦　稱有意見指他無出席部分國際會議","createTime":"2017-05-21T05:27:19.000Z","updateTime":"2017-05-21T05:32:23.000Z","uid":20933,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"6a3e238fe319e6cd7d6126361494d2f60e08930e","tid":251589,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-21T05:27:19.000Z","msg":"教育局局吳克儉表示，雖然只餘下6個星期任期，但政府在教育方面無放軟手腳。<br />\n<br />\n吳克儉在出發前被問到，為何不留港處理BCA全港性系統評估、防止學生自殺委員會建議等政策問題，而要繼續外訪，吳克儉回應，最近有意見指他無出席部分國際會議，所以要跟日常工作取得平衡。他又說，現屆政府做了不少事，並非是個人的工作，各項工作都有相關同事處理，例如跟進防止學生自殺委員會去年年底提出的建議。<br />\n<br />\n另外他又說，本港教師曾燕紅成功登上珠穆朗瑪峰頂，是香港人和學生的榜樣。<br />\n<br />\n吳克儉與兩名助理出訪英國倫敦，將探訪當地兩所大學，並與正在倫敦升學的香港學生和商界人士會面。"},{"pid":"5db9f0d912cb77cfe03f3bf44a8765765aa01cad","tid":251589,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-21T05:27:33.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1331530-20170521.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1331530-20170521.htm&d=4vQCcaBbFH%2F4J6PBkjxGnu9M5Ue6CDmcYDZznX2R1Ws%3D&h=7ef5db39\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1331530-20170521.htm&h=96d360ef\" target=\"_blank\">http://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1331530-20170521.htm</a>"},{"pid":"56941ae825b2a209a37817ab0bfcf3fc3afe9f47","tid":251589,"uid":40628,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-21T05:32:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://cdn.thestandnews.com/media/photos/cache/10922450_10153106112599714_6761725377573506348_n_OIolZ_1200x0.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thestandnews.com%2Fmedia%2Fphotos%2Fcache%2F10922450_10153106112599714_6761725377573506348_n_OIolZ_1200x0.jpg&h=6b2d8e30&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n香港人去埋挑戰南極添 , 唔撚講嘅 ?"}]}